# 8. GitHub Custom Domain Configuration

After configuring DNS, I returned to GitHub and added the custom domain inside:

```text
Repository → Settings → Pages → Custom Domain
```

The domain entered was:

```text
cithost.com
```

GitHub then verified the DNS records and connected the custom domain successfully.

