# 9. HTTPS / SSL Certificate

Once the custom domain was connected correctly, GitHub automatically generated an HTTPS certificate for the website.

The following option was enabled:

```text
Enforce HTTPS
```

This ensured that the website became securely accessible through:

```text
https://cithost.com
```

